yContaineruniface_104trj1665703206355.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/trj1665703206355.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/trj1665703206355.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"trj1665703206355\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Adds an attribute to a start element tag.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"trj1665703206355__topic_d136637e1_d136638e1_d136639e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104trj1665703206355_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"trj1665703206355__codeblock_ewz_2dh_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ADDATTRIBUTE(Name, Value, Indent)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"trj1665703206355__section_gjp_fdh_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162843e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">ADDATTRIBUTE parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__4\">Attribute name; maximum length is 40\n                        bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__4\">Attribute value; maximum length is 512\n                        bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Indent</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__2\"> Boolean </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"trj1665703206355__table_d16298e1_d16299e1_d16300e1__entry__4\">Indicates whether the attribute should start on\n                        a new line with indentation spaces prefixed, or that it should be added to\n                        the previous attribute or element start tag separated only by a\n                        space.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"trj1665703206355__section_qqv_ndh_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162843e150\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"trj1665703206355__p_d136721e1_d136722e1_d136723e1\">Values returned:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"trj1665703206355__ul_hyb_pdh_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trj1665703206355__li_d48317e1_d48318e1_d48319e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> Success. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trj1665703206355__li_d48320e1_d48321e1_d48322e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">–1</code> Failure. Called in an illegal\n               sequence. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"trj1665703206355__section_wzs_pdh_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162843e172\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"trj1665703206355__p_d136655e1_d136656e1_d136657e1\">This operation can occur only immediately after an\n            invocation of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span>, because attributes can be added only to\n            the start tag of an element.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104trj1665703206355_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"trj1665703206355__codeblock_kpn_rdh_hwb