", 1) uxml2->addAttribute(\"attr2\", \"ValueB\", \"true\") uxml2->addAttribute(\"attr3\", \"ValueC\", \"false\") Copy Result: Explain this code <ElementA attr1=”ValueA” attr2=”ValueB” attr3=”ValueC” Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}